    "name": "MT-III 'Pointman'",
    "gameVersion": "0.2.50.10",
    "mass": 25482,
    "creationDate": "1945.09.02",
    "class": "",
    "desc": "Considering the 'Salt' a dead-end for tank design, a new family of vehicles was devised. Two designs was planned that would replace the Salt and Hardhat tanks. Sharing common parts, this would improve costs and logistics of specialised vehicles. The result was 'Pointman' and 'Marsktank', both highly modern and relatively cheap, they were well liked by their crew and officers.",
    "cost": 26764
  },
